<HL>
   IMF Plans Loans
   And Rates Linked
   To the Price of Oil
   ----
   By Peter Truell
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
                                                                                                       

</HL>
<DATE>
09/19/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A24
</SO>
